chrome.runtime.onStartup.addListener(function() {
    chrome.action.disable();  
});
```
Currently this is only a "duct tape fix", just to get things up and running at all. Ideally, all [extension lifecycle](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions/develop/concepts/service-workers/lifecycle) stuff from common.js and chrome.js should go here. Ref. [Migrate to a service worker](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions/develop/migrate/to-service-workers).

Also [replaced some unsupported APIs](https://developer.chrome.com/docs/extensions/develop/migrate/api-calls) and was able at least get the context menu item partially working:

